      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2 for this factor.",
      "rationale": "Formal model input uncertainty quantification is not required at MRL 2. Nominal input values (viscosity, density, hematocrit) are well-characterized for bovine blood at 37 °C and sourced from peer-reviewed literature. Factor is not assessed per the MRL 2 assessment plan."
    },
